  }, "Our engineers love it"), mdx("p", null, "From an engineering perspective, it\u2019s extremely efficient having our projects centralized in one platform. In the past, every time I updated a project, I had to manually sync my designs through a plugin into a third-party \u201Cinspection\u201D platform where engineers would have access to. Although this method works, it\u2019s not ideal in a fast-paced project development."), mdx("p", null, "With Figma, engineers see changes in real time, allowing them to participate in every step of the project, from wireframes to design."), mdx("p", null, "Design Programmatically is key for us, so our engineers can simultaneously work on developing components while us, designers, progress with the design creation and copywriters progress with content. We essentially have all of the tools we need to create dynamic, digital products in one place."), mdx("h2", {
